- [ ] Let each member explain responsible parts
- [ ] Upload the video to YouTube/Google Drive
- [ ] Paste the video link on the front page of the report

## Suggested video structure

1. Introduction: "This is Hoppr, a UTM Ride Hailing App for verified UTM users."
2. Explain Progress 3 scope: High fidelity prototype, GitHub, Trello, video.
3. Student user demo: login, ride booking, payment, delivery, profile.
4. Driver user demo: dashboard, available jobs, accept/decline, trip execution, earnings.
5. Admin demo: verification and reports.
6. GitHub demo: show README table linking modules to scripts.
7. Trello demo: show tasks and member responsibilities.
